{"tid":1320928,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「慈悲為懷」3322 學生可以 $2450 一年報讀能仁大學！","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:42:10.000Z","uid":112551,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"775c82ed0af7bf80e662ca4941038dd676ed7bae","tid":1320928,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jjedxP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jjedxP.png&h=a1b7d22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 如果NMTSS （免入息審查資助計劃）申請獲批准，扣減政府資助後，全年只需繳交$2,450*(分2期繳交) (低於HK$10,000完成整個4年制學士學位課程)。<br />\n<br />\n* 此一優惠不適用於非HKDSE學歷申請者及本身已經獲得HKDSE 33222成績<span style=\"color: red;\">但已持有學士學位之申請人</span>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能上年免學費，啲人都爭相去報讀能仁，搞到今次要制止各位連登仔。但可見能仁一直受連登學生追棒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，名額有限呀！"},{"pid":"686ca6620e844270bc0c979b17e5c420df9cc29c","tid":1320928,"uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"唔係應該 能仁畀返錢我哋?"},{"pid":"1b81016b0509aba561885ba8936c136a82782fab","tid":1320928,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"你恆大可以升到大學<br />\n我能仁一樣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fd0c12c16c87516495b91be2a03d852170b9fc","tid":1320928,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"能仁所不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1b28cb4866f547587ce935e80233d3cec95b08","tid":1320928,"uid":200739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"能大喲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0369b6cc7ffabd8b3f2766a9b93366b6a297366c","tid":1320928,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:03:30.000Z","msg